title: MyDadsHotGirlfriend - Marie McCray
description:
Marie McCray could sure use some help putting together the shelves she just bought. Her boyfriend promised to help, but he's too busy at the office to keep his promises. What's a helpless girl to do? She calls over her boyfriend's son to help her put it together. He's so strong and handy with tools. Marie decides maybe she needs someone younger in her life, someone who can fulfill all her needs, and her boyfriend's son is just that person. She may not know how to handle a wrench, but Marie she sure knows her way around her boyfriend's son's big hard tool.
